						<summary>

						<p>Slab in a field called Yeḷamakki belonging to the Mūkāmbika temple of Kollūru.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">14th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This record is badly worn out and only the imprecatory portion of the writing can be made out. It seems to have registered a grant.</p>						

						<p>It is in characters of the 14th century A.D.</p>						

